In [7]:
def plot_missing_data(df):
  try:
    columns_with_null = df.columns[df.isnull().sum() > 0]
    null_pct = (df[columns_with_null].isnull().sum() / df.shape[0] * 100).sort_values(ascending=False)
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.barplot(y = null_pct.index, x = null_pct, orient='h', palette='Blues')
    plt.title('  Column    (%)', fontsize=16)
  except:
    print('   .')

In [14]:
def transform_year(year):
  if year < 100:
    if year <= 20:
      year += 2000
    elif year >= 80:
      year += 1900
  return year
In [15]:
df['Year'] = df['Year'].apply(transform_year).astype('int')

In [41]:
df_na_platform = df.groupby(by=['Platform'])['NA_Sales'].sum().reset_index()
df_eu_platform = df.groupby(by=['Platform'])['EU_Sales'].sum().reset_index() 
df_jp_platform = df.groupby(by=['Platform'])['JP_Sales'].sum().reset_index() 
df_other_platform = df.groupby(by=['Platform'])['Other_Sales'].sum().reset_index()

df_total = df.groupby(by=['Platform'])['Total_Sales'].sum().reset_index() 

df_total = df_total.combine_first(df_na_platform).combine_first(df_eu_platform).combine_first(df_jp_platform).combine_first(df_other_platform)
df_total = df_total.set_index('Platform')
In [42]:
df_na_platform_category = df.groupby(by=['Platform_category'])['NA_Sales'].sum().reset_index()
df_eu_platform_category = df.groupby(by=['Platform_category'])['EU_Sales'].sum().reset_index() 
df_jp_platform_category = df.groupby(by=['Platform_category'])['JP_Sales'].sum().reset_index() 
df_other_platform_category = df.groupby(by=['Platform_category'])['Other_Sales'].sum().reset_index()

df_total_category = df.groupby(by=['Platform_category'])['Total_Sales'].sum().reset_index() 

df_total_category = df_total_category.combine_first(df_na_platform_category).combine_first(df_eu_platform_category).combine_first(df_jp_platform_category).combine_first(df_other_platform_category)
df_total_category = df_total_category.set_index('Platform_category')

sales_platform_year = df.groupby(by=['Year', 'Platform'])['Total_Sales'].sum().reset_index()
is_sales_top = sales_platform_year.groupby(by=['Year'])['Total_Sales'].transform(max) == sales_platform_year['Total_Sales']
topsales_platform_year = sales_platform_year[is_sales_top].reset_index(drop=True)

platform = topsales_platform_year['Platform']

plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
trends = sns.barplot(x='Year', y='Total_Sales', data=topsales_platform_year, palette='Blues')

index = 0
for value in topsales_platform_year['Total_Sales']:
    trends.text(index, value + 1, str(platform[index]), color='black', size=10, ha="center")
    index += 1
